Tabulate method outputs

Source: R/utilities.R
dot-TDDTable.Rd

Helper function to tabulate sortable data in package vignettes.

.TDDTable(Table, dat, ...)

Arguments

Table

DT::DataTable() or an equivalent tabulation function.
dat

Matrix or vector of data to be tabulated, with (row) names corresponding to the methods employed.

Value

.TDDTable() produces a table plotted using Table().

Author
